{"tid":1938611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"捷榮有員工初步確診 2名同事檢測亦陽性","createTime":"2020-03-22T16:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T16:17:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c3411dacdea0ef961485d34bd5ed6de97796c59b","tid":1938611,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"餐飲服務供應商捷榮國際控股表示，上周五獲悉1名銷售部員工初步確診新型冠狀病毒，之後自行安排與該名員工有緊密接觸的34名員工，到私家醫院或診所進行病毒檢測，有2人結果初步呈陽性、14人呈陰性，其餘預計本月25日前收到初步檢測報告。<br />\n<br />\n捷榮表示，相關員工未有接觸集團的生產線，生產過程亦沒有受到影響，而仍未收到檢測報告的員工，將會在家隔離。<br />\n<br />\n集團會按衞生署建議，確保座位間有足夠的距離，每位員工上班時都亦需要量度體溫及進行消毒。 捷榮亦表示，獲悉有員工初步確診後，已即時聘請清潔公司，以最高規格消毒確診員工的工作樓層。<br />\n<br />\n復工撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d0d33246d2ca7e69b8c71e5311edae7d46eb62","tid":1938611,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"茶記D奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff73b46f0f404fdba0f0e1bd33ae877358a878bf","tid":1938611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adeef3bda6e2b88651fe7c3abadb3bbd1d7fe3e5","tid":1938611,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d0d33246d2ca7e69b8c71e5311edae7d46eb62","tid":1938611,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"茶記D奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"沙士咖啡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\